actors:
CREATE TABLE actors (
	id int,
	first_name text,
	last_name text,
	gender text
)
directors:
CREATE TABLE directors (
	id int,
	first_name text,
	last_name text
)
directors_genres:
CREATE TABLE directors_genres (
	director_id int,
	genre text,
	prob float
)
movies:
CREATE TABLE movies (
	id int,
	name text,
	year int,
	rank float
)
movies_directors:
CREATE TABLE movies_directors (
	director_id int,
	movie_id int
)
movies_genres:
CREATE TABLE movies_genres (
	movie_id int,
	genre text
)
roles:
CREATE TABLE roles (
	actor_id int,
	movie_id int,
	"role" text
)
